Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:10.55,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我为了不让其毁坏而太过于珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:16.47,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也输入邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:22.34,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又将其删除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.74,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这样的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.91,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}将其打破的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.75,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}为我带来契机的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:35.73,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心将其紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:39.31,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}将现在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.80,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}虽然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.67,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使将碎片全部收集齐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.87,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必须用自己的双手将其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.57,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}极其珍视的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.92,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕将其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:02:01.61,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:04.89,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}都存在于此
